{
  "stem": "10825.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he came in to his apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When he lived there, his apartment was-- but-- so he came in to the apartment where he lived.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he found there somebody else living, a gentile.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is my apartment.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, we have to do something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, where did you buy those medals, in Tashkent, on the bazaar, on the market?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it took something, so he gave him a push or-- or-- he killed him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a funeral.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was, kill Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was the-- the dessert after Babi Yar, that 100,000 Jews were killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said that all-- there were only Jews were killed in Babi Yar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they never wrote and they never said that it was Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, that's-- and we came there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we saw it from a-- from our house where we lived, we saw what-- what was happening until it-- it was-- and then we lived-- we went-- the choir [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was resolved.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all the gentiles who came from Lutsk went back to Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They found their families, maybe richer than they were before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we couldn't go back to Lutsk, because there was a grave of 18,000 where all our families or some other were killed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This-- my brother, Zeylik.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I met one, a survivor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, oh, your brother went with the-- with the ones that went Thursday.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a Thursday that they took 3,000 men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they brought them in a certain place, and they killed them all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we couldn't return to Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How did you find out about what happened to the families in Lutsk?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, through survivors, through people that-- that we met after the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
